OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,FThe family of a woman who was killed
OL,7,Fby a driver with a serious eyesight
OL,8,Fcondition are campaigning for
OL,9,Fcompulsory eye tests for drivers.
OL,11,FMarie Cunningham, 79, was killed in
OL,12,FSouthport in November 2021 as she and
OL,13,Fher friend, Grace Foulds, 85, were
OL,14,Fcrossing the road.
OL,16,FHe daughter Sue described her mum as a
OL,17,Fsocial butterfly. She said: "She was
OL,18,Fone of nine so you could imagine her
OL,19,Fsocial life. Her calendar was always
OL,20,Ffull."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
