OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,FThe driver, then-65-year-old Glyn
OL,7,FJones, was repeatedly told not to
OL,8,Fdrive by healthcare professionals, but
OL,9,Fhe continued anyway without telling
OL,10,Fthe DVLA or his insurer.
OL,12,FHe was jailed for seven years in 2023
OL,13,Fand banned for driving for nine years
OL,14,Fand 10 months, having pleaded guilty
OL,15,Fto two counts of causing death by
OL,16,Fdangerous driving.
OL,18,FSue said: "This man could not see his
OL,19,Fown hand in front of his face."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,F"He drove by peripheral vision. He
OL,7,Fthought it was a bag of rubbish
OL,8,Fbecause a newspaper went down the side
OL,9,Fof his window," her brother Terry
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,F"If Glyn Jones had done the right
OL,13,Fthing and hung his keys up, it
OL,14,Fshouldn't be to the families but mum's
OL,15,Fdeath could have been avoided. Grace's
OL,16,Fdeath could have been avoided."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
