OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,FMarie's family now lead the 'Sight
OL,7,FSafe' campaign, calling for compulsory
OL,8,Feye tests to be introduced every 10
OL,9,Fyears for drivers at each licence
OL,10,Frenewal.
OL,12,FThe Department of Transport is
OL,13,Fcurrently asking for public opinion on
OL,14,Fproposals to introduce mandatory
OL,15,Feyesight tests every three years for
OL,16,Fdrivers aged 70 and over, but Marie's
OL,17,Ffamily say this is not enough.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,FSue said: "We're asking for every
OL,7,Fdriver to have an eye test, every 10
OL,8,Fyears when they renew their driving
OL,9,Flicence.".
OL,11,FDenise Voon, from the College of
OL,12,FOptometrists, said they support the
OL,13,FDepartment of Transport's push for eye
OL,14,Ftests for over 70s, but said they
OL,15,Fcould go further.
OL,17,FShe said: "The College of Optometrists
OL,18,Fwould like to see mandatory eye
OL,19,Ftesting for all drivers, at licence
OL,20,Fapplication and renewal."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,FAn inquest into the deaths of Marie
OL,7,Fand Grace, along with two other
OL,8,Fpedestrians, found that around 2.1
OL,9,Fmillion UK licence holders may not
OL,10,Fmeet the legal standard to drive
OL,11,Fbecause of a lack of regular testing.
OL,13,FTerry said: "This never started out
OL,14,Fwith picking on older drivers. Glyn
OL,15,FJones was 65, and was told for a
OL,16,Fminimum of 10 years before that, so he
OL,17,Fwould have been in his 50s."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,FSue said: "If the system would have
OL,7,Fworked, my mum would still be here. I
OL,8,Fdon't want to hear that another family
OL,9,Fhave gone through this."
OL,11,FA spokesperson from the Department of
OL,12,FTransport said: "This was a tragic
OL,13,Fincident, and our thoughts are with
OL,14,FMarie's loved ones.
OL,16,F"We know driving is important for
OL,17,Folder people's independence, but this
OL,18,Fmust be balanced with safety.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777075397
OL,3,C'Sight Safe': Family's campaign after
OL,4,Cmum killed by driver with bad eyesight
OL,6,F"That's why we are consulting on
OL,7,Fmandatory eyes tests for drivers over
OL,8,F70 through our Road Safety Strategy,
OL,9,Fand developing options for cognitive
OL,10,Ftesting for older drivers."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
